Let’s encourage 💪 young people to think positively about their bodies and the way they look, and defeat self-doubt 🏹

Let's celebrate individuality and #StopTheBeautyTest

#HappyDusshera 

#Dove #DoveIndia #DoveBeauty #SelfLove #BodyPositivity #DoveSelfEsteemProject #ConfidentBeauty #EmpowerYouth #LetsChangeBeauty

We need to teach our children that beauty is a state of mind.
If we value ourselves, it doesn’t matter what the world says – we can walk with confidence.

We’re working to build self-esteem and confidence in young people all over the world through the Dove Self-Esteem Project 🌍 so all girls can feel empowered and are able to drive social change for a better future – however that may be 🙌

In 2004, we turned this vision and mission into the Dove Self-Esteem Project. We work with leading experts in the area of body image to develop evidence-based tools. We’ve reached over 82 million young people globally with self-esteem education so far, and together we can reach millions more.
 
Download our free resources tools for parents, mentors, teachers, and youth leaders to build positive body confidence in young children via using the 🔗 link in bio. 
 
#Dove #DoveIndia #DoveBeauty #BeautyIRL #BeautyTest #SelfLove #BodyPositivity #DoveSelfEsteemProject #ConfidentBeauty #EmpowerYouth #LetsChangeBeauty

When it comes to the relationship between social media and low body confidence, seeking validation via likes and comments, and making comparisons to others can also have a negative effect. One of the main causes for this is that many of the photos we see online 🤳 are digitally distorted and not representative of real life. ​

​We know how much influence media and brands hold in defining our thoughts, #DoveIndia is striving to create an authentic and confident tomorrow 🙌 ​for the youth. ​

​Join us to change the narrative of beauty and love our real selves 💪​​

#DoveSelfEsteemProject is committed to empowering 8 million young people by 2025. 

#Dove #DoveIndia #DoveBeauty #BeautyIRL #BeautyTest #SelfLove #BodyPositivity #DoveSelfEsteemProject #ConfidentBeauty #EmpowerYouth #BodyPositiveMovement

At Dove, we’re on a mission to encourage 💪 young people to think positively about their bodies and the way they look, enabling them to reach their full potential in life.
 
🔎🔎 "Words can have a huge impact on our self-esteem, and constantly talking negatively about our bodies can reinforce the idea that there is only one type of body shape that is beautiful. It’s a pattern we have to break if we want our children to grow up to be confident about the bodies they’ve got."  - Jess Weiner, Body Image Expert
 
Instead of objectifying and marking adolescents on their physical appearance🙅‍♀️, let’s change the narrative of beauty for generations to come, for empowered and confident youth. 

Take a pledge with us🤝, using the link in bio 🔗 to #StopTheBeautyTest and put an end to this. 

#Dove #DoveIndia #DoveBeauty #BeautyIRL #BeautyTest #SelfLove #BodyPositivity #DoveSelfEsteemProject #ConfidentBeauty #EmpowerYouth #LetsChangeBeauty
